snippet: A well-liked Twin Falls bartender found dead in a home with one of her five children and her longtime boyfriend recently obtained an order of protection against the man, who police say likely killed the mother and daughter and then himself....

headline.print_headline: Police: Boyfriend Likely Killed Idaho Mother, Teen
headline.main: Police: Boyfriend Likely Killed Idaho Mother, Teen

lead_paragraph: A well-liked Twin Falls bartender found dead in a home with one of her five children and her longtime boyfriend recently obtained an order of protection against the man, who police say likely killed the mother and daughter and then himself.
